54struct GPACTRL_BITS { // bits description
55 Uint16 QUALPRD0:8; // 7:0 Qualification sampling period for GPIO0 to GPIO7
56 Uint16 QUALPRD1:8; // 15:8 Qualification sampling period for GPIO8 to GPIO15
57 Uint16 QUALPRD2:8; // 23:16 Qualification sampling period for GPIO16 to GPIO23
58 Uint16 QUALPRD3:8; // 31:24 Qualification sampling period for GPIO24 to GPIO31
59};
60
61union GPACTRL_REG {
62 Uint32 all;
63 struct GPACTRL_BITS bit;
64};
